HEADWORD: Hypobole
<hw>Hy*pob"o*le</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ a
throwing under, a suggesting; <?/ under + <?/ to throw.]</ety>
<fld>(Rhet.)</fld> <def>A figure in which several things are mentioned
that seem to make against the argument, or in favor of the opposite
side, each of them being refuted in order.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

